data.description: Welcome to Mills River… This Residential and Commercial property is less than 10 minutes from the Asheville Regional Airport, shopping, restaurants, and a wide range of amenities, sitting atop a hill in the heart of Mills River, this property offers beautiful views, sunrises, and sunsets.  Masterfully designed one story, wide and open floor with chef’s kitchen, soaring 12' ceiling with huge windows in main living area.  Beautiful fireplace allows you to live and entertain in style.  High-end touches are evident throughout this home with 3.44 of commercial/residential rolling landscape usable land, this property offers elegance and opportunity.   This property would be great for horses or simply enjoying the land in its natural state.  Less than 10 mins to the WNC ag center, less than 20 minutes to downtown Hendersonville, & 30 min to Tryon International Equestrian Center.   “Please do not pull into driveway without appointment”.
